data.description: The subject property is a 2,660 sq. ft mixed use building on Metropolitan Avenue in Middle Village. The property consists of two (2) 1 bedroom apartments, one (1) 2 bedroom apartment and 3 retail stores. The property is conveniently located on the busy shopping street, Metropolitan Avenue, in the heart of Middle Village. The property has growth potential.
